{"tid":758966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又爆升！2022/23年度公營房屋建屋量創新低 僅1.48萬個單位","createTime":"2018-07-28T07:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T02:49:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e91dbd1052be3e1f6f5b41c29ab66f6f7d4245f9","tid":758966,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"公屋輪候冊多達27萬宗申請，一般家庭要等最少5.1年才上樓。房委會最新數字顯示，2022/23年度公屋建屋量跌至只有1.33萬個單位，連同1,500個資助出售房屋單位，該年度建屋量只有1.48萬個單位，創近年新低，數字更比長策要求公營房屋每年平均建屋量2.8萬個單位大減。<br />\n<br />\n房委會在網頁更新2018/19年度至2022/23年度，公營房屋建設計劃的單位數目。最新數字顯示，未來5年公營房屋建屋量一直未達長策目標，本年度只有可供應約2.71萬個公營房屋單位，當中包括6,600個資助出售房屋單位。直至2022/23年度，公屋房屋建屋量將跌至只有1.48萬個單位，當中只有1,500個資助房屋，數字創近年新低，單位數目較長策目標尚欠1.32萬個單位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180727/58493993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F58493993&d=Qs%2FWYXSXxEG7f5jIpYGn3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=6ee00332\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F58493993&h=9fdb0b79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180727/58493993</a>"},{"pid":"294d2ff34d99963329db3e5a38322e24746e5f76","tid":758966,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"一億港元一平方吋 不是夢"},{"pid":"1ecba8a25f3264dbf612e51eb94d1ac3bbc0d05e","tid":758966,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"294d2ff34d99963329db3e5a38322e24746e5f76","tid":758966,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"一億港元一平方吋 不是夢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"樓本位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d2fb6a0651339d7ede430ebd854ae4f07ceb42","tid":758966,"uid":151496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re